To Encrypt:
  1. Enter 3 rotor names to be used as their numbers ideally ranging between 0 to 4.
  2. Enter 3 offsets each corresponding to their respective rototrs.
  3. Enter the string to be ciphered.
  4. Note the ciphered string.


To Decrypt:
  1. Enter 3 rotor names to be used as their numbers ideally ranging between 0 to 4.
  2. Enter 3 offsets each corresponding to their respective rototrs.
  3. Enter the ciphered string to be deciphered.
  4. You will see the deciphered data.
